{"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of input text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"input text","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTextInput","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllTextInputComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TextInputComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"input text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Inout text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of colors ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"borders (from "},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"), spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and  dimensions (from "},{"code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:borders:colors:spaces:dimensions:)"],"title":"Initializers","generated":true},{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/borders","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/colors","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/dimensions","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/sizes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"title":"Instance Properties","generated":true},{"anchor":"Default-Implementations","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/TextInputComponentTokens-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for input text component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the text input component tokens you want.","","        override var sizeMaxWidth: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._3000 }","","        override var spacePaddingBlockDefault: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineSmall }","","        override var colorBorderEnabled: MultipleColorSemanticToken { colors.repositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","","        override var borderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.widthMedium}","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider: TextInputComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(textInput: CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    OrangeTheme(textInput: CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeDimensionSemanticTokensProvider for dimensions","    let inputTextComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, border, color, space and _ semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let inputTextComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                space: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                dimensions: CustomDimensionSemanticTokensProvider())"]},{"name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.17.0"}]}],"type":"aside","style":"note"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"class","title":"OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B37ThemeTextInputComponentTokensProviderC","roleHeading":"Class","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo","identi